        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: PLCB2 was detected in Liquid chromatography-mass spectrometry results of LDCVs.\nFigure 2B: Post-embedding immunogold (inset) staining against PLCB2 displays localisation on the surface of LDCV.\n\n18/01/2021 Dnyanada: The paper does not provide any information on the specificity of the antibody used.. Experimental description: No mention of mouse strain used ...Authors were contacted for retrieving this information (15/05/2020 Dnyanada, xu.zhang@ion.ac.cn)" ;
